{"name":"Trench Croaker","size":"huge","type":"beast","tag":"mutated","alignment":"unaligned","hitDice":"17","armorName":"natural armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":5,"otherArmorDesc":"15 (natural armor)","speed":"20","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"40","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"152 (16d12 + 48)","speedDesc":"20 ft., swim 20 ft.","strPoints":"18","dexPoints":"8","conPoints":"16","intPoints":"5","wisPoints":"10","chaPoints":"5","blindsight":"60","blind":true,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"6","customCr":"5 (1,800 XP)","customProf":3,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The shambling mound can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The shambling mound regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the shambling mound can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the shambling mound can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The shambling mound can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the shambling mound's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the shambling mound's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the shambling mound dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Amphibious","desc":"The [MON] can breathe air and water (and ink)."},{"name":"Transluscent","desc":"The [MON] has advantage on stealth checks while submerged."},{"name":"Light Absorption","desc":"Whenever the [MON] is subjected to radiant damage, it takes no damage and regains a number of hit points equal to the radiant damage dealt."},{"name":"Electroreceptive","desc":"The [MON] is blind, but has tremorsense out to 60ft due to electroreception. If the [MON] takes lightning damage, it is blinded for one round."},{"name":"Bioluminescence","desc":"The [MON] emits eerie light. A creature who looks directly at the [MON] must make a DC 15 wisdom save or be charmed until the end of the [MON]'s next turn. While charmed, the creature is incapacitated and invisible to every creature except the [MON]. Once a creature saves, it is immune to this effect for 24 hrs."}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"The [MON] makes one Tongue attack, one Bite attack, and one Swallow (if applicable)."},{"name":"Bite","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 2d8] piercing damage and the target is grappled."},{"name":"Tongue","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 15 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 1d8] bludgeoning damage and the target is pulled 15ft towards the [MON]."},{"name":"Swallow","desc":"The [MON] swallows a medium or smaller creature grappled by it. The swallowed target is blinded, restrained, and unable to breathe, and it must succeed on a [CON SAVE] Constitution saving throw at the start of each of the [MON]'s turns or take [3d6] acid damage. If the [MON] moves, the swallowed target moves with it. The [MON] can have up to 2 creatures swallowed at a time.\n\nA swallowed creature is able to breathe for a number of rounds equal to their constitution score (modified from RAW), however speaking (or casting a spell with verbal components) depletes their air. A creature can try to escape by succeeding on a DC 20 strength check. Additionally, if the [MON] takes 20 or more damage in a single turn from swallowed creatures, it must make a DC 15 constitution saving throw or regurgitate all swallowed creatures."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Ink Sacs (Recharge 6)","desc":"The [MON] cries viscous ink from its eyes. All creatures (and vehicles) within 20ft (and in water) have their speed reduced by 4 times."}],"reactions":[{"name":"Chase","desc":"When a creature moves, the [MON] can take one move action in pursuit."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[{"name":"stealth","stat":"dex","note":" (ex)"}],"damagetypes":[{"name":"bludgeoning","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"cold","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"lightning","note":" (Vulnerable)","type":"v"},{"name":"radiant","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"}],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[{"name":"prone"}],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":5,"damage":[]}